snippet.title: Camila Cabello, Aishwarya Rai B & Katherine Langford sharing Runway | L'oreal Paris Le Défilé
snippet.description:
Camila Cabello is world famous singer and also an actress.

Aishwarya Rai Bachchan is Miss World 1994 and also very famous Indian Actress.

Katherine Langford is an Australian actress. she had her breakthrough starring as Hannah Baker in the Netflix television series 13 Reasons Why, which earned her a Golden Globe Award nomination

These personalities together sharing a runway at "Le Défilé L'Oréal Paris" 2021 and then some cute pictures and videos makes our day.
